    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">MIT OCW 18.S096 + 15.450 (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">A <strong>stochastic process</strong> is a sequence of random variables indexed by time. Finance models asset prices as stochastic processes because tomorrow's price depends on today's, plus noise you can't predict.</p>
    </div>

